full_text:
Yeah, my hands were just too big to get underneath to sneak a peek at
the screenprinted labels. I had to cut all the antenna leads (easy
fix) and desolder the two wire bundles with the white and grey wires.
After that I was able to lift the board enough to see under there. It
was a bear, no doubt. Honestly I just couldnt get my fingers far
enough under the board with cutters to ensure I was cutting the right
wire. 

thanks
Andy

